Welcome to Dokuwiki Mobile Client ******************************************************************************************************************IntroductionThe current version is a client that allows a user to connect via the desktop, fetched Dokuwiki version via XML-RPCand output the result to the screen.My current effort is to make a simple one-button app that fetches the version via the Titanium Mobile.I have divided the tasks into three parts:Task 1 >>> The app fetches Dokuwiki version via XMLRPC over HTTP (Online browsing) on Titanium MobileTask 2 >>> The app fetches Dokuwiki version via XMLRPC over HTTPS(Online browsing) on Titanium MobileTask 3 >>> The app fetches Dokuwiki version via XMLRPC over HTTPS(Offline browsing) on Titanium MobileGetting Help*******************************************************************************************************************If you have a question or need help with Dokuwiki Mobile Client, you can get help from the following sources:* eMail: finmikie@gmail.com* IRC: irc://irc.freenode.net#stripesnred